I like country music. I don't cook. I love to cook and bake everyday. I live on a farm in a rural area. I cook a lot of typical Indian cuisine. I would like to have an Indian cuisine business. I like the winter season the best. I am from the South of India. I like warm summer weather. I love Serena Williams. I play a lot of sports but mostly tennis. I like that tennis builds muscle and stamina. It makes me very tired. I drive trucks for a living.,Hi I dont cook but I like jamming to country music. What do you like doing? I basically cook and bake everyday absolutely love it. Oh thats cool I live in rural area with farm so I relate so much with cooking. I usually cook typical indian cuisine. Thinking of turning it into a business. I like winter in all 4 seasons which one do you prefer the most? Well I am from the south of india. So I like warm summer weather. I play sports of all sorts. Tennis mostly. Love serena williams! Thats nice but I do drive trucks as my job so thats very tiring already for me.,test_691_1
I'm a fan of older country music that I grew up listening to. I grew up in a city in the 1990s and I'm not a fan of country music. I like rock and metal music. I am in a relationship with another person. I'm a big fan of rock music but don't really like death metal music. I'm in a relationship with a man. I own a working farm. I like to share my crops with friends and family. I've gained some weight recently. I enjoy playing tennis.,"I like the older country must. Mostly, because it's what I grew up listening to. A lot of the newer music sounds more like pop music. I like Garth Brooks, Tim McGraw and Darius Rucker. Do you listen to country?  Not very much, but an older lady in the city I grew up in used to listen to it when she watched us neighborhood kids in the '90s, so I am very familiar with Garth Brooks, Tim McGraw, and others. Darius Rucker I mainly only know from Hootie and the Blowfish. Do you like any other kinds of music? I do. I enjoy rock and metal. My partner is in a rock band, so lately I've been listening to a lot, especially when driving. That is wonderful. I love rock. I like some metal but I have never been able to get into death metal. Does your partner sing or play an instrument in the band? He write, he sings and plays rhythm guitar - he's quite busy. The band is called EXHALE, if you'd be interested. The most popular song is Count The Days. There's a music video and everything!  Wow, that is great. I will look it up! How is the farm? Do you have animals or crops? Or both? There is both, chicken, ducks, pigs, goats. We do corn and strawberries, pumpkins. I hear that, it's tough getting old! I eat one baked good and I feel like I gain 10 pounds.",test_691_2
"I can't cook, but my husband can. I have a husband. I own a farm. I love cooking and baking. Our farm grows produce and has chickens for eggs. I have 14 chickens. I use their eggs in my baking. I make a lot of rice. I hope to open a business using my cooking skills someday.","Definitely the food, though it's wasted on me since i can't cook. My husband is a great cook, though! Do you eat a lot of what you grow/raise?  I love cooking/baking personally. I do. We mostly just deal with produce, but we have some hens for our eggs. Eggs straight from a chicken is the best. I agree. I've always kept chickens myself. Currently we have 14.  My baking is so much better with their eggs. Mostly a lot of rices. I cook primarily Indian food and it's a lot of rice. Haha! Now that is funny. Maybe you can give my husband some cooking lessons in Indian cuisine.  I would love to. I'm hoping to run a business one day with my cooking.",test_691_3
I am not good at cooking. I am familiar with cooking. I am familiar with cooking devices. I have never used a pressure cooker. I have used a pressure cooker before. I am married to a man that likes to cook. I am impatient. I am familiar with pressure cookers. I have a husband who likes Asian food.,"I'm going to try a new recipe tonight. Want to hear about it? I'd love to, but you're gonna have to explain to me how things work because as you know, I'm not a cook at all! No problem. I am planning to make dahl using a pressure cooker to ensure the lentils are soft and delicate. Then make a pilaf rice and some tandoori chicken. I wish I had a tandoor though.   No, a tandoor is a special type of oven which they use in India to make tandoori chicken. It helps give it its flavour. It is made from clay. Oh I see! I've never used a pressure cooker before. Does it cook other things other than lentils? I hear it makes the cooking go much faster. Yes, you can do lots of things in pressure cookers like stews and soups. Most of the time, I use it to soften meat. I love putting my lamb shanks in there. It makes the meat fall right off the bone. Do you have a pressure cooker? I don't, but hearing what you're saying makes me want to purchase one for my husband. He's an avid cook but sometimes that makes the cooking process a lot longer than I want! I would recommend a pressure cooker. It is a great item for beginner cooks. You throw it all in, pop the lid on and wait for the whistle really. I gave one to my sister for Christmas and she uses more often than me now. He likes to cook asian food. Lots of prep work. But I'm a big fan of the end results most of the time!",test_691_4
I participated in debates. I am a vegan. I loved to swim when I was young. I have always loved playing with animals. I used to be a veterinarian. I travel for a living. I love to go on cruises. I have my own blogs. I am a cruise ship singer. I hate politics. I don't believe in politics. I didn't like to debate. I love politics.,"Fine too,i was busy with debate preperation. I was busy being an angry vegan,making some food. I love swimming when I was young what about you? I used to love playing with animals,still do. I used to be veterinarian,now I travel the world. Great, what I love to do here is going on cruises. I sing on cruise ships,and write about it on my blogs. Not really I hate politics I just dont believe in them never have.",test_693_1
I am going to go on cruise. I love cruises. I go on the cruise. I love it too. I have a blog  about vegan recipes. Another debate will be next week. I'm interested in trying some new recipes. I participated in debates few days ago. I travelled last year. I went to Greece. I saw lots of animals. I'd love to do a European cruise or one around the Hawaiian islands. My last cruise was in the Western Caribbean. I was on a cruise around the Hawaiian islands. I wish I could have gone sooner in my life.,"yeah, I have started getting into blogging about vegan recipes. when was the last time you participated in debates? A few days ago.  I have another one coming up next week.  So whats your latest vegan recipe on your blog?  I'm interested in trying some new recipes too! I went to Greece. It was a fun trip and I saw loads of animals which was a bonus. Where did you go for your last cruise? We did the western caribbean.  It was so beautiful and fun.  I'd love to do a European one or one around the Hawaiian islands! You should, I could probably get you some sort of discount for travel because of my job.",test_693_2
"I work in a lounge on a cruise ship. I like whale-watching. I want to go to Alaska. I have been to Greece. I think Greece is a beautiful country. I don't enjoy being around a lot of tourists. I am a singer. I have been to Hawaii. I like to sing classic songs that people know. I like to swim. I would like to take a cruise to Hawaii. I think Hawaii is a gorgeous place. I tried surfing when I was young, but never got good at it. I enjoy viewing fish and wild animals. I enjoy scuba diving. I think learning to surf is hard. I think fish is delicious to eat. I do not fish. I place high value on all life. I am a vegan.","As soon as the cruise lines open up again, I'd like to go to Alaska!  I'd love to go whale-watching whenever I'm not working in the lounge. That sounds like a lot of fun! Is there a certain time of year that is best for whale watching? I've heard Summer is the best time.  It would be great to see something different, my last trip was to Greece which was beautiful but full of tourists.. Do you sing different music depending on where the ship is traveling? I imagine people would want that if you are visiting Hawaii. What about Alaskan songs?  You know that's a great question!  I'll have to look up some Alaskan songs.  I usually do the classic favorites that people always request, and then we'll feature some local performers to show off the culture of the region.  We had some beautiful dancers come on board and perform when we toured Hawaii. Oh, that is lovely! I really need to book a Hawaiian cruise! I am ready to get my swimming game on again! Oh you definitely should! It's so gorgeous there.  I know you love to swim, have you ever been surfing?  There are tons of classes you can take there! Haha! I think I fell off the board a few times when I was younger! Have you become a surfing pro with all that time at sea? I gave it a try, but it was a lot harder than I thought.  I preferred the diving classes, there are so many cool fish and other animals to see. Haha no I could never fish, even as catch and release. When I visited Hawaii though everyone ate fish and my friends said it was the best they ever had.  I'm sure when you visit you could pick up some new recipes to try.",test_693_3
I am trying to eat healthy because I am going on a cruise and want to look good. I own a grill. I'm trying to eat healthy. I love fish and food. I am a vegan. I get bored of food when dieting. I love eating potato chips. I have to limit buying potato chips because I have poor impulse control.,"I think I'm going to try a new recipe for salmon for dinner tonight.  I need to stay in shape so when I finally do get to go a cruise I'll be looking good! Well I am going to make salmon on the grill, with lemon and dill! I am going to make a kale salad to go along with it. I am not sure how it will taste but it is healthy! I bet the salmon will be great for you since you love fish. I've had good kale and bad kale, so it's a coin flip! You going to be able to keep this up? Honestly, I am not sure. I love food so much. Do you have any tips for maintaining? You must have a very healthy diet being a vegan. I think I get bored of the food easily when I am dieting. I need to switch it up. Do you have any exciting recipes? I make some really good kale chips. They are healthy, crunchy, and tasty. Those sound any good> Whatever seasoning you want. I like curry, jerk, and lemon-pepper. Just toss with a little oil and bake in the oven OK, I will definitely try it! Potato chips are my downfall, so this sounds like a much healthier alternative.  I don't even buy chips. If they are here, I eat them all. So I just don't even let them in the home.",test_693_4
I drink alcohol. I do not like dealing with customers. I am a mechanic. My father was a farmer. We are expecting a baby. My dad was an alcoholic. I am in a relationship. My name is Mark. I have two older brothers. I am not sociable.,"It's what gets me through the day as a mechanic dealing with customers. We have a baby coming I'm hoping it won't be alcoholic like me and dad. Well, I just would prefer that this kid turns out right unlike the rest of us. My main problem is dealing with other people.",test_694_1
