I like gardening. I like to listen to music. I like to garden. I like to listen to music. My sons birthday is on Christmas. I have a son. I have been married for fifteen years. I would like to become a farmer. I am a car salesman.,"Yes, that seems like a good deal. You get all that in one. I usually listen to music while gardening. Do you? Yes, I like to listen to music when I garden also. When is your sons birthday? My sons birthday is in  April. How long have you been married for? 15 years! I can't believe how fast it's gone by! That is crazy. They say time goes fast when you are having fun. How do you like being a cars salesman? It's a job. I think I'd rather be a farmer but land is so expensive. People will always need cars though, I think...",test_763_3
I grow strawberries. I grow vegetables. I grow lettuce. I grow peaches. I live in California. I eat a lot of the things I grow at home. I am a vegan. I am not a vegan or vegetarian. I like barbecues food. I used to eat veggie burgers. I eat plant-based patties at barbecues. I only have one more veggie plot. I have a wife. I am thinking of growing black beans. I have used beets in veggie patties. I like roasted radishes. I have a son.,"My strawberries are starting to come up, any luck with your vegetables? They're looking great. They're a bit labor intensive and finicky but I think I've got the hang of it now. Oh definitely! It makes life a lot easier because the produce at my local grocery store isn't the best. The California weather must be perfect for growing all kinds of produce. That is good. I was thinking of becoming vegetarian and but I do like barbecues food. What do you normal eat at barbecues? Yes, I have noticed there is a lot more vegan and vegetarian options available in the shops now than there was before. I am thinking of growing black beans, the ones they use in the vegan patties, but my wife doesn't want me to use the last veggie plot for them. Yes she does. Yes, I may recommend that to her. She likes beets in her salad so she might like that option. What about radishes? Do you think they could be used? Ok. I will keep that in mind. Thank you. What is the things that your son likes to plant in the garden?",test_763_4
I like to read. I like to coupon. I live in the city. I like to take evening walks. I live in the city. I like to walk. I have a job that I walk to. I have 3 rats. I have 5 dogs. I enjoy pilaties. I take a pilates class. I go to college. I like to paint. I have 1 brother. I like to paint family potraits. I want a portrait of my brother and I. I am in debt with college tuition. I charged 5000 for a painting of 2 people. I have 5000 dollars. I am a good painter and worth the 5000.,"Hi I'm good, I mainly like reading coupon books to find the best deals. You shop in the city, I do cause thats where I live. I do, don't you love walks at sunset in the city? They are my favorite. Yes, I do, I walk alot, especially to work. Same here, I have to with five dogs and then the three rats, they are very active. Lol, three rats? I gotta run in a few, pilates class (my favorite). Yea, I stay busy, my brother's on the phone (my only brother). I would love to paint you and your brother. I'm very good at family portraits.. I would, my prices start at $5000(need to pay my full-time college tuition) let me know. I might have that in my petty cash drawer, let me check. Trust me you won't regret this. Can't put a price on family.",test_767_1
"I have a brother. I am a painter. I am painting a portrait for the other speaker. I like finding coupons. I painted a portrait of Elton John with his dogs. I love painting regular people. I went to art school. I have student debt. I paint for professionals. I have pets. I have a painting of my pets. I don't think rats are cute. I have 5 dogs. I have pet rats. I have a great dane, 2 German shepherds, a pit bull, and a mutt.","I am excited for the portrait that you will be doing of me and my brother.  Have you found any good couponing deals lately? I can't wait to do that painting for you. No I haven't found any good coupons lately, but I hope to find some good ones soon. I did a painting for Elton John and his dogs awhile back I was star stuck, but I managed to get through it. Oh, yes. Art school isn't cheap, but I have more and more professionals asking me to paint for them after that. I love painting regular people better it is just more fun. You deserve it. Hopefully the interest keeps up. I would love to see a painting of your pets. Have you ever done a self portrait with all of your pets?  Yes, it was the first really big one I did. It was how I realized I love to paint portraits. That sounds adorable! I don't think I have ever seen a family portrait with rats before. I have never understood how some people don't think they're cute. They are great little pets. But I did leave them out of the painting. Just the 5 dogs since the rats don't stay still. I have a grant Dane, two German shepherds, pit bull, and a mixed we are not sure what he is.",test_767_2
I own some dogs. I take them to the park. I don't have any dogs. I adopted my dogs from the shelter. I might want a pitbull. My favorite dog breed is an Akita. I own a pitbull. I was bitten by a dachshund and chihuahua. I was bitten by my friend's rat terrier. I used to work at a daycare for dogs. I don't like the dog named Maggie. I paint. I go to school. I own five dogs. I am working on speaker 1's portrait.,"They are very playful and energetic! I love taking them to the park and watch them run around happily. I really want a dog some day.  Did you adopt them all? I have certain breeds that I love such as Akitas but those would only come from a breeder.  I have no real preference but maybe a pittie just because people still have negative impressions of them. Pitbulls are lovely! My pitbull is very kind and sweet, like a giant teddy bear. For me, it is all about the owner raising the dog right. Definitely true. The only dogs I've ever been bit by were a dachsund and a chihuahua.lol Same here. My friend's rat terrier bit me once and I didn't even notice until I realized the dog was hanging on my arm. I used to work at a doggie daycare and the meanest dog there was a rat terrier named Maggie.  I love dogs but Maggie...not so much. I wish I could work at a doggy daycare but between my five dogs, school and painting my life would get a little too crazy, haha. Yup, your portrait is taking more time than I expected it to!",test_767_3
I paint portraits. I have multiple pet rats. I have multiple dogs. I am getting kittens. I have multiple dogs. I prefer to get pets from a shelter. I like Persian cats.,"Have you finished painting my portrait? Not yet but i will definitely finish it soon but i can tell you look really good in it.  I can't wait! How long does it usually take to do a formal portrait? Have you been keeping busy with other things? It varies from months to years if you want you know what i mean but it really depends on how much are you putting in. I got some other portraits to work on but my dogs is sick so i'm taking care of it more now. Vet did a good job but it take sometime for him to recover but yeah my other dogs are treating him pretty well, laying around him and licking him more even my rats looks worried for him. He'll nbe fine for sure. How are your petss? As much as I think certain breeds of cats are really smart or pretty, I think I'm just going to see what they have at the shelter. I think it's important to rescue pets when you have a chance, rather than have breeders introduce new ones. I've always loved cats, and kittens can be so playful. I hope the process moves quickly. Getting it from the shelter is an awesome decision. Yeah my hands are full but if i could ever get a cat, it would definitely be a Persian.   Haha that would be a Tom and Jerry scene in my house if i get a cat. i always think they are like secret life of pets when I'm not around. I'm pretty sure you will those love those cute fur balls. ",test_767_4
I like to eat steak. I run. I cook for myself. I will visit my parents for Easter. My parents live in Alaska. I celebrate Easter. I am visiting my family for Easter. I sometimes wear dresses. I have a family. I am a woman. I work as a programmer. I don't visit my parents very often. I try to visit my parents as often as I can. My mom bought me a new car. I like my new car.,"I just finished eating some steak. So yummy. Oh yeah. I did after I finish running this morning. I plan to go visit my parents in alaska. I will be spending it with my family as well, and showing off my new dress! But I thought you were visiting your parents? So you work as a programmer? Oh yeah I only visit my parent very few times. I visit as much as possible. My mom got me a new car so you know... It is, but now she wants me to visit almost every day! It can be a lot.",test_769_1
"I will be visiting my parents, whom I don't see very often. I will be flying to Alaska for Easter. I have a job. I will have to do work on my flight. I have a mom who will help me out. I am not a good cook and sometimes have  trouble in the kitchen. I will cook ham for Easter. I am a good cook but it took practice. I love savory pies.","I just booked my flight to Alaska for Easter! My parents will be happy we can spend some time together over the holiday, since I don't see them very often. Goodness, I am not even sure! I certainly have plenty of work I need to do on flight. Our new interns make more work than they are worth.  My mom will want to introduce me to all of her neighbors and I am sure she has a big Easter dinner planned. What about you? Do you have to cook the ham since your mom bought the car? hahaha :) Oh definitely. She's not going to let me off the hook. But she's a softie so she will end up helping me out as I'm kind of a hot mess in the kitchen. Do you have any tips for me for becoming a better cook? Alright, so maybe I will not let my mom help me as much this time. What's so great about brown sugar?? I love savory pies. Do you know how to make those?",test_769_2
I have a Lexus ES 350. I have a toyota Corolla. I will be seeing family for Easter. My family is not nearby. I like apple pie. My mom makes apple pie.,"I have a Toyota Corolla with many many mmiles on it. It gets me from A to B and is dependable so I can't complain! That's great! I hear Lexus is manufactured by Toyota, so they use the same parts and all that. It's nice that your mom is able to help you out! I wish my parents were closer, but it sounds like we both will be seeing family for Easter!! Flight is out of Chicago. Not really sure how long it will be, depends on my connecting flights ANNNDDD if they change my flights. I've learned to be flexible when flying! Yes!! Midway is just too small to get deals out of. The time should go fast tho as I'll be catching up on some work and of course looking forward to some good Easter food! What's on your menu? Sounds like a productive flight! Other than ham, we'll bake up some meat pies, empanadas, and quiches! Heyyy! That sounds great!!! I'm a fan of my mom's apple pie. What do you serve for dessert? We're doing apple pie too! Made by my mom, of course!",test_769_3
I have 28 cousins on my mother's side. I have a large family. I work as a programmer in Chicago. I do not have a large family. I work freelance. I am from Alaska.,"Alaska was great, not ready to leave yet! Oh yes, I have a big family. My mom has 7 siblings and each of them have many kids as well. I think I have about 28 cousins from my mom's side. Do you have a big family? Wow!  That's a huge family.  It's just me and my parents for Easter.  Did you do most of the cooking? That's fun! I did not do most of the cooking. When I was home with my family, all the elderlies liked to take on all the cooking. So I just let them be and instead enjoyed the time with my cousins. I will stay for another 3 days and then fly back to Chicago. I have to go back to my demanding programming job. What do you do for a living? I'm a freelancer mainly.  Growing up I didn't have a lot of family members around me like you to help me decide on a career path.  I envy your large family, and I bet cooking is a big deal in your family with so many mouths to feed.  What are some of your traditional family dishes? Oh my mom wanted me to stay back in Alaska when I graduated high school but I thought I wanted to explore the ""outside"" world more. They didn't really help me decide on my career path, so you're definitely  not losing much there! My grandmother has this really great cranberry pie recipe, so every Easter my aunts and my  mom will make a dozen of the pie to feed everyone of us! Mmm...  That cranberry pie sounds amazing.  My mom has a killer appie pie recipe of her own.  I'm sure it has to be a team effort to bake all those pies. Yes, we have cranberry pies every time we get together-- Thanksgiving, Christmas and Easter. It is a tradition without fail every year. Apple pie sounds really yummy, would love to try that next time I visit you. Does your mom ever go to the orchard and pick fresh apples for the pie?",test_769_4
I like Ska. I like Sublime. I work as a doctor's assistant. I am in college and I don't work. I went to college in the past and enjoyed it. My mom runs the college. I go to the local college. I take coaching classes in college. I don't really enjoy other sports. I really enjoy fishing. I am an only child. I am also an only child. I own a condo near the beach and I love the ocean. I attend parties in the dorms.,"I love sublime! What do you do for a living? I'm a doctor's assistant. What about you? I'm unemployed at the moment while I'm in college. Ah, what college? I miss my college days! The one in my home town because my mother runs it. Coaching classes because I play soccer. Nice. I've never been much for sports. Unless you consider fishing a sport! I do. So, any brothers or sisters? I'm an only child. Same here. Wish I had a brother to fish with growing up though. I love the ocean. Just bought a condo near the beach. Party central! Right on! I've been partying at the dorms.",test_77_1
I like the band Sublime. I also like the band Sublime. I like to listen to waves at the beach. I'm studying at college. I did well on my finals. I'm a doctor's assistant. I enjoy baroque music.,"I love so many of their songs, it's hard to pick a favorite. Santeria is a good one though, have you heard it? Is that the one about wine? or am I thinking of a different song. No, when I'm on the beach I like to just listen to the waves. It's very soothing. Where do you usually listen to their music? Usually when I am doing my studying for college. It helps me relax and focus on my studies. It even helped me get through my finals this past month.  I did very well thank you for asking. I have my music to thank for that, really helped me absorb the knowledge from my studying.  I understand that. WHen I was studying to be a doctor's assistant, I used to put on Baroque music. Yes, it has the same beat as a human heart at rest so it helps to keep from getting stressed.  It's going pretty well my boss is really funny.",test_77_2
